    {
      "chinese": "當男孩到了青少年時，他們就會到聚會所學習部落的事務。到了十五歲的年齡時，部落的幹部就會帶領他們學習體能訓練、潛水、撒網捕魚、敬老尊賢、參加歲時祭儀、學習歌舞等等。",
      "ab": "Yo masakapah to ko fa’inayan, itini to i taloan a minanam cangra to tatayalen no niyaro’. Tangasa to to safaw lima ko mihecaan, misaselal to. Keriden no mama no kapah misaloma’, micelem a mifoting, mitafokod, mingodo to mato’asay, mikapot to ilisin, minanam to kero ato radiw.",
